{"id":17215,"title":"Outbreak of serial knee joint sepsis after arthroscopic surgery: a case series with the guideline for treatment.","abstract":"Knee infection after arthroscopic surgeries is rare but devastating complication. A serial knee joint infection occurred in our hospital after the contamination of arthroscopic equipments set with an unknown microorganism. Herein we describe the natural course of these patients and suggest a treatment protocol according to the experiment gained from management of these patients. ","date":"2014-06-06","categories":"Bacterial Infections and Mycoses","split":"train","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/24901863","annotations":[{"name":"Microorganism","weight":0.883265,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Microorganism"},{"name":"Sepsis","weight":0.877753,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sepsis"},{"name":"Therapy","weight":0.751095,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Therapy"},{"name":"Complication (medicine)","weight":0.734358,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Complication_(medicine)"},{"name":"Surgery","weight":0.697426,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Surgery"},{"name":"Infection","weight":0.666263,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Infection"},{"name":"Hospital","weight":0.657965,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hospital"},{"name":"Joint","weight":0.523998,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Joint"},{"name":"Knee","weight":0.40323,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Knee"},{"name":"Arthroscopy","weight":0.40272,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Arthroscopy"},{"name":"Experiment","weight":0.26328,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Experiment"},{"name":"Medical guideline","weight":0.250837,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Medical_guideline"},{"name":"Septic arthritis","weight":0.0546925,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/S